    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Crisis Signal Detector\\n\",\"**NLP Project 80 of 100** — Detect urgent or distress-like messages for escalation in social/support platforms.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\\nfrom sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression\\nfrom sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, classification_report, f1_score, average_precision_score\\nfrom sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42; rng = np.random.default_rng(SEED)\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Synthetic crisis vs normal messages\\nnormal = ['How do I reset my password?','When does the sale start?','Can I change my order?','What are your hours?',\\n          'Thanks for the quick response!','Where is my package?','Great product!'] * 30\\ncrisis = ['I feel completely hopeless and alone','Please help me I am in danger','I cannot take this anymore',\\n          'Someone is threatening me','I need immediate help this is an emergency',\\n          'I feel unsafe at home','My child is missing please help'] * 10\\n\\ndf = pd.DataFrame({'text': normal + crisis, 'crisis': [0]*len(normal) + [1]*len(crisis)})\\ndf = df.sample(frac=1, random_state=SEED).reset_index(drop=True)\\nprint(f'Shape: {df.shape}, Crisis rate: {df[\\\"crisis\\\"].mean():.1%}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(df['text'], df['crisis'], test_size=0.2, random_state=SEED)\\ntfidf = TfidfVectorizer(max_features=5000, ngram_range=(1,2))\\nX_tr = tfidf.fit_transform(X_train); X_te = tfidf.transform(X_test)\\n\\nlr = LogisticRegression(max_iter=500, random_state=SEED, class_weight='balanced')\\nlr.fit(X_tr, y_train)\\ny_pred = lr.predict(X_te)\\ny_prob = lr.predict_proba(X_te)[:,1]\\n\\nprint(f'Accuracy: {accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred):.4f}')\\nprint(f'F1: {f1_score(y_test, y_pred):.4f}')\\nprint(f'PR-AUC: {average_precision_score(y_test, y_prob):.4f}')\\nprint(classification_report(y_test, y_pred, target_names=['Normal','Crisis']))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Crisis detection requires high recall** — missing a real crisis is unacceptable.\\n\",\"- **Class weighting is essential** for the heavily imbalanced distribution.\\n\",\"- **For production, route flagged messages to human responders immediately.**\\n\",\"- **Include crisis hotline information** in automated responses.\\n\",\"- **Regular model auditing** prevents bias and missed signals.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
